1.0.0.name: wordpress/promote-mdn
1.0.0.description:
Based on freediver's SEO Smart Links, Promote MDN automatically links keywords and phrases to MDN pages. They keywords, phrases, and pages are supplied by a special page on MDN

MDN is the best online resource for web developers, by web developers. Promote MDN helps your readers discover and learn about web technologies on MDN.

To help code on this plugin, go to Promote MDN on Github.

Translations available: de_DE, es_ES, fr_FR, nl_NL, pl_PL, pt_BR. To help translate this plugin, go to the MDN Verbatim page.
